<div class="mt-5  border-b border-gray-200">
  <div>
    <label for="email" class="px-1 block text-base font-medium text-gray-700">Recipeint emails<span class="text-xs"> (comma separated)</span></label>
    <div class="mt-1">
      <input type="text" name="email" id="email" class="shadow-sm focus:ring-indigo-500 focus:border-gray-500 block w-full sm:text-base border-gray-300 rounded-md" placeholder="you@example.com, friend@example.com">
    </div>
    <div class="sm:col-span-6 mt-3">
      <label for="about" class="px-1 block text-base font-medium text-gray-700">
        Message to recipients
      </label>
      <div class="mt-1">
        <textarea id="about" name="about" rows="10" class="shadow-sm focus:ring-indigo-500 focus:border-gray-600 block w-full sm:text-sm border-gray-300 rounded-md" placeholder="Hey everyone,&#10;Please download this file at your earliest convenience!&#10;&#10;Regards,&#10;Your Teammate"></textarea>
      </div>
      <div class="clearfix block mt-5">
        <button type="button" class="ml-5 float-right items-center px-6 py-3 border border-transparent text-base font-medium rounded-md shadow-sm text-white bg-orange hover:bg-orange focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-orange">
        Send to recipients
        </button>
        <button type="button" class="float-right items-center px-6 py-3 border border-transparent text-base font-medium rounded-md shadow-sm text-white bg-gray-500 hover:bg-gray-700 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-gray-700">
        Clear Form
        </button>
      </div>
      <div class="clearfix"><p class="float-right w-80 text-sm mt-1 text-right">After clicking 'Send to recipients', you will receive e-mail documentation of this file share.</p></div>
      <div class="my-3">
        <p class="text-gray-600"><b>What now?</b></p>
        <p class="text-gray-600 w-96">You can track the recipients with whom you've shared the file and whether or not they have downloaded it via the 'Tracking' tab.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
